<p><font color="#669900"><b>KDE - The Comfortable Desktop</b></font></p>
<p>SUSE LINUX comes with the latest version of the versatile KDE desktop. Play CDs with the file manager Konqueror or prepare data backups with the burning application K3b. Send e-mail with KMail or enjoy yourself with the KDE games. KDE comes with an extensive range of software: administration, multimedia, games, development, networking, and more. One desktop for all!</p>
<p>In addition to KDE, the SUSE CDs feature GNOME and an impressive selection of other popular window managers like ctwm and Blackbox.</p>
